%!PS

40 40 scale % Change the scale of the page

5 5 translate % Change the origin

/newSquare {
    newpath
    0 0 moveto
    0 1  rlineto % Up
    1 0  rlineto % Right
    0 -1 rlineto % Down
    -1 0 rlineto % Left
    setrgbcolor % Change color
    fill % Fill the shape with said color
} def

1 0 0 newSquare

1 1 translate

0 1 0 newSquare





